       <p style="padding-top:0px;">
        <strong>
         <a href="https://youtu.be/IT9HlBOeKKc" target="_blank">
          CVE Working Groups, What They Are and How They Improve CVE
         </a>
        </strong>
       </p>
       <p>
        Community members actively engage in six CVE WGs to help improve quality, automation, processes, and other aspects of the CVE Program as it continues to grow and expand. In this episode, the chairs and co-chairs of each WG chat about their WG&rsquo;s overall mission, current work, and future plans.
       </p>
       <div style="font-size:100%;text-align:right;padding-top:12px">
        <a href="https://youtu.be/IT9HlBOeKKc" target="_blank">
         Listen Now &gt;&gt;
        </a>
       </div>
      </div>
      <td style="width:1%; vertical-align:top; height: 272px;">
      </td>
      <td class="callout2" style="width:39%; vertical-align:top; height: 200px;">
       <div class="tablehead" id="Become a CNA">
        <a class="nounderline" href="cve/cna.html" title="Become a CNA">
         <span class="whitefont">
          Become a CNA
         </span>
        </a>
       </div>
       <div>
        <table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:100%;">
         <tr>
          <td style="verticalalign:top; padding-top:0px; padding-right;20px;">
           <a href="cve/cna.html">
            CVE Numbering Authorities
           </a>
           ,
           <br>
           or &ldquo;CNAs,&rdquo; are essential to
           <br>
           the CVE Program&rsquo;s success
           <br>
           and every
           <a href="about/terminology.html">
            CVE Record
           </a>
           is added
           <br>
           to the
           <a href="cve/index.html">
            CVE List
           </a>
           by a CNA.
           <br>
           <br>
           <strong>
            Join today!
           </strong>
           <ul>
            <li>
             <a href="cve/cna.html">
              Business benefits
             </a>
            </li>
            <li>
             <a href="cve/cna.html">
              No fee or contract
             </a>
            </li>
            <li>
             <a href="cve/cna.html">
              Few requirements
             </a>
            </li>
            <li>
             <a href="cve/cna.html">
              Easy to join
             </a>
            </li>
           </ul>
           <br>
           <br>
           <br>
          </td>
          <td style="font-size:89%; text-align:center; verticalalign:top; padding-bottom:0px;">
           Total CNAs:
